{"tid":2130876,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【唔想幫襯血汗工廠?】10 大網購黃店總彙","createTime":"2020-07-29T12:44:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T03:31:20.000Z","uid":263303,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5583f2ea5dfe877d3c748f72324053cc2281d4b6","tid":2130876,"uid":263303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T12:44:27.000Z","msg":"記得上年想幫襯黃色經濟圈網購，但由於仲係起步階段，無論光時定係重光號既貨品選擇都偏少。近日由於柒婆禁餐廳堂食，上網一睇先發現黃色網購圈貨品選擇豐富左好多。所以如果唔想揀血肉工廠（兼 $800 先送貨）既 Mall 既話，其實仲有大把更好既選擇。<br />\n<br />\n今日整理左個短 list 比自己做紀錄，雖然一定唔齊，但應該好過無。<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>1. 重光號 x 同人辦館 <a href=\"https://ourhkmall.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fourhkmall.com%2F&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6erBpkLuHOqafswNxXmn3gI%3D&h=034203cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ourhkmall.com/</a> </strong></ins><br />\n免運費門檻: 買滿 $500<br />\n送貨時間: 2-4 星期<br />\n貨品分類: 口罩、糧油雜貨、家居用品、護理保健、護膚化妝、母嬰用品、文具書本<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"teal\">&gt; 咁多間入面個網頁做得最靚，介面搜尋等都好易用，最鍾意佢碌落去就有得睇貨，唔洗不斷按下一頁</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n &gt; 零食選擇有大路野之餘都有啲細 brand<br />\n &gt; 有香港品牌 section ，好似辣殺、Year 28、少爺麥啤咁<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>2. 瓹窿瓹罅 <a href=\"https://www.guruguruhk.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.guruguruhk.com%2F&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6erBpkLuHOqafswNxXmn3gI%3D&h=32c05437\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.guruguruhk.com/</a></ins></strong><br />\n免運費門檻: 買滿 $300（買滿 $450 有上門環保回收服務）<br />\n送貨時間: 無特別寫明<br />\n貨品分類: 零食、飲品、美容潔膚、寵物、嬰兒、環保<br />\n<span class=\"teal\"> &gt; 免運費門檻咁多間最低，買兩包「光城香米」已夠數</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n &gt; 有本地貨 section <br />\n &gt; 盛惠 $98 既2020愛情運勢網上推算 + 流年網上運程<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>3. 蟹貨倉 <a href=\"https://www.crabwarehouse.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.crabwarehouse.com%2F&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6erBpkLuHOqafswNxXmn3gI%3D&h=b27f6ca0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.crabwarehouse.com/</a></ins></strong><br />\n免運費門檻: 買滿 $300 （健身用品除外，要買滿 $550 先送）<br />\n送貨時間: 2-3 星期<br />\n貨品分類: 口罩、健身用品、瑜伽用品、家居清潔、黃色產物、<br />\n<br />\n &gt; 主打強身健體貨品<br />\n &gt; 防具同口罩選擇呢間最齊<br />\n &gt; 啞鈴、阻力帶、甚至健身椅都有<br />\n<span class=\"teal\"> &gt; 愛國用品及 TEE 令人驚喜，大推！</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>4. HMarket <a href=\"https://www.hmarket.com.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hmarket.com.hk%2F&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6erBpkLuHOqafswNxXmn3gI%3D&h=45cd8f66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hmarket.com.hk/</a></ins></strong><br />\n免運費門檻: 買滿 $500<br />\n送貨時間: 1-2 星期<br />\n貨品分類: 口罩、零食、飲品、美容、環保<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"teal\"> &gt; 口罩選擇多，豬咀同濾器都有</span><br />\n &gt; 零食同野飲有唔少係英國貨<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>5. 支援在台手足代購平台</ins></strong><br />\nSupport_twbro <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/supporttwbro\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsupporttwbro&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6erBpkLuHOqafswNxXmn3gI%3D&h=3f80eb92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/supporttwbro</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://Yellowbirds.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FYellowbirds.hk&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6erBpkLuHOqafswNxXmn3gI%3D&h=9cdf9f43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Yellowbirds.hk</a> <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/yellowbirds.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fyellowbirds.hk%2F&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6erBpkLuHOqafswNxXmn3gI%3D&h=e82ae3f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/yellowbirds.hk/</a><br />\n台灣維城士多 (即將開幕) <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/victoriastoreTW/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FvictoriastoreTW%2F&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6erBpkLuHOqafswNxXmn3gI%3D&h=be5c69a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/victoriastoreTW/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>6 YellowDims <a href=\"https://yellowdims.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyellowdims.com%2F&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6erBpkLuHOqafswNxXmn3gI%3D&h=325cff8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://yellowdims.com/</a></ins></strong><br />\n免運費門檻: 搵唔到邊到有寫...<br />\n送貨時間: 無特別寫明<br />\n貨品分類: 口罩、食物、飲品、文創、時裝、成人用品、良心義賣<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"teal\"> &gt; 有分平台集運同黃店派送</span><br />\n &gt; 有唔少本土細 brand<br />\n &gt; 同其他網購比，多左時裝、成人用品、良心義賣<br />\n &gt; 除左零食之外，有少量急凍肉、海鮮蒸氣火鍋等食物<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>7.光時 <a href=\"https://www.hkongs.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkongs.com%2F&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6erBpkLuHOqafswNxXmn3gI%3D&h=e813c30c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkongs.com/</a></ins></strong><br />\n免運費門檻: 買滿 $500<br />\n送貨時間: 2-3 星期<br />\n貨品分類: 零食、飲品、家品、護理、寵物、藥物健康<br />\n<br />\n &gt; 最老字號既黃店網購，但貨品選擇唔算好多<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>8. 香城雜貨 <a href=\"https://www.heungshingonline.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.heungshingonline.com%2F&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6erBpkLuHOqafswNxXmn3gI%3D&h=452052fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.heungshingonline.com/</a></ins></strong><br />\n免運費門檻: 買滿 $400<br />\n送貨時間: 無特別寫明<br />\n貨品分類: 主打食品及飲品，另有好少量的餐具及家居清潔用品<br />\n<br />\n &gt; 個網 load 得有少少慢，貨品選擇唔係好多<br />\n &gt; Made in HK 版面既貨，係其他網店似乎搵唔到<br />\n &gt; 做緊買滿 $100 加 $120 換口罩既優惠<br />\n &gt; 有賣香城迷你奶黃月餅<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>9. 黃色港口 <a href=\"https://www.yellowporthk.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yellowporthk.com%2F&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6erBpkLuHOqafswNxXmn3gI%3D&h=aa2abde6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.yellowporthk.com/</a></ins></strong><br />\n免運費門檻: 搵唔到邊到有寫...<br />\n送貨時間: 無特別寫明<br />\n貨品分類: 零食、醬料、手工啤、文創、時裝、寵物用品、護膚品<br />\n<br />\n &gt; 有本地貨 section <br />\n &gt; 手作精品選擇比較多<br />\n<strong><ins><br />\n10. 煲底市集 <a href=\"https://www.stand-with-hk.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stand-with-hk.com%2F&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6erBpkLuHOqafswNxXmn3gI%3D&h=78885bc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.stand-with-hk.com/</a></ins></strong><br />\n免運費門檻: $350<br />\n送貨時間: 無特別寫明<br />\n貨品分類: 口罩、零食、醬料、寵物用品、廚具<br />\n<br />\n &gt; 有賣黃色手作精品"},{"pid":"6dd373fc5123b21f3b223a05cebf41691c65964c","tid":2130876,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T12:45:43.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d98d8d4baf758aa6ccf1f45387445381a3e4226","tid":2130876,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T12:47:06.000Z","msg":"高汁"},{"pid":"4a17110df5b4c13a6817e7927c525729bac15811","tid":2130876,"uid":37397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T11:19:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/9/98/%E5%A4%8F%E9%9B%A8%EF%B8%B0%E5%8A%89%E6%98%8E%E4%B8%80%E8%BA%AB%E8%9F%BB.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/340?cb=20100407045608\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F9%2F98%2F%25E5%25A4%258F%25E9%259B%25A8%25EF%25B8%25B0%25E5%258A%2589%25E6%2598%258E%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E8%259F%25BB.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%2Fscale-to-width-down%2F340%3Fcb%3D20100407045608&h=ad63215f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"109b51ba8de83912d15b020190635e85692d93ea","tid":2130876,"uid":175679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T11:42:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c20360e